                {"number": 2, "title": "Write Your Message", "instruction": "On the small paper, write a brief message to your deceased loved one. Be specific. Ask a question you genuinely need answered, or say what you never got to say. Fold the paper small.", "duration": "10 minutes", "note": "The SPR found that specific, heartfelt communication was far more likely to receive response than vague requests"},
