                {"number": 5, "title": "Speak the Invocation", "instruction": "Hold the bound feather over your heart. Speak the invocation aloud, then state the name of your deceased loved one three times. Place the feather before the photograph.", "duration": "3 minutes", "note": "Speaking the name is essential. In spiritualist tradition, the name is the call."},
                {"number": 6, "title": "Enter the Listening State", "instruction": "Sit back. Soften your gaze on the candle flames. Breathe slowly. Your task now is simply to wait and listen. Notice any sensations—temperature changes, sounds, images in your mind, emotions that arise. Do not judge or analyze yet.", "duration": "30-60 minutes", "note": "Authentic communication often comes as impressions rather than clear words. Trust what you receive."},
