                {"number": 8, "title": "Test the Communication", "instruction": "If you receive a clear message, test it. Ask a follow-up question—something specific that only your loved one would know. If the response is accurate, you have genuine communication. If vague or wrong, it may be your own subconscious or interference.", "duration": "5-10 minutes", "note": "Katherine's Huguenot heritage insisted on testing. Never accept blindly."},
                {"number": 9, "title": "Close the Vigil", "instruction": "When ready to close (or at dawn if doing a full vigil), ring the bell three times. Say: 'The vigil ends. I release you with love. The door closes gently. Go with my blessing.' Extinguish the red candle, then the white.", "duration": "5 minutes", "note": "Proper closing is essential. The door between worlds must be consciously shut."},
